ViewProxy
=========

A private, local-only Chrome extension for streaming an exact page region
into a floating proxy window.

Optional video-PiP path includes patterns derived from Google LLC Apache-2.0
Picture-in-Picture samples and ideas from Crop PiP (JKH-ML, Apache-2.0).

This project:
  - does not load remote code or assets
  - does not phone home
  - injects only when you click the extension or use a shortcut
  - stores only local crop preferences in chrome.storage.local
